In re Resignation of Fister.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Fister (1987), 33 Ohio St. 3d 601.]

(D.R. No. 87-6 Decided October 21, 1987.)

The resignation of William E. Fister from the practice of law in the state of Ohio is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
